[[div_ class="panel"]]
++ Soldier

**Requirements:**
* **Must be Male**
* **SkullSelect:** 98th Percentile or Higher
* **Intelligence Quotient:** 95 or Lower

**Description:** Help President GREP and ğ• AI CEO Fritz Williams defend the Earth against the Jaywalker threat. 30 ğ•Coins per hour. If you die in combat, you will be immortalized as a GREP Virtual Avatar which may be purchased from the ğ•Store.
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="panel"]]
++ AI Training Beauty Model

**Requirements:**
* **Must be Female:** chromosomal verification required.
* **Age:** 18-24
* **SkullSelect:** 90th Percentile or Higher
* **Sexual Marketplace Value:** 98th Percentile or Higher.

**Description:** Let us GREP you! Provide valuable training data in the form of images of your delectable body. 1 ğ•Coin per image! Note that this position may lead to SkullSelect penalties as a result of out-of-wedlock relations.
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="panel"]]
++ AI Data Labeler

**Requirements:**
* **SkullSelect:** 70th Percentile or Higher
* Lack of disgust response.

**Description:** Label and classify images, text, audio, and other media for GREP. 10 ğ•Coins per hour. Emesis bags are not provided.

[[/div]]

[[div_ class="panel"]]
++ Pavement Layer

**Requirements:**
* **SkullSelect:** 50th Percentile or Higher
* Visible abs required.

**Description:** Got some muscle? Help us drain and fill in the remainder of the Pacific Ocean surrounding the former Hawthorne Island! You'll receive a generous salary of 7 ğ•Coins per hour!

[[/div]]

[[div_ class="panel"]]
++ Organ Donor

**Requirements:**
* **SkullSelect:** 25th Percentile or Higher
* Must be same race as recipient to avoid miscegenation. Note that since 2067, the 'One Drop' Rule applies.

**Description:** Selling organs can be a lucrative means of getting out of debt! Organs can sell for as much as 100,000 ğ•Coins apiece! As thanks, you may receive a GREP-generated card from the ğ• AI shareholder whose life you've helped prolong!

[[/div]]

[[div_ class="panel"]]
++ Advertising Recipient

**Requirements:**
* **SkullSelect:** 5th Percentile or Higher
* Must have functional eyes and ears.

**Description:** Watch ads for a reward! Earn 1 ğ•Coin for every hour of ğ• AI advertising watched!

[[/div]]





